<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-32-1205 </DOCNO><TEXT>A risk assessment is made on the programming technique used by ENEL (ItalianElectricity Board) for medium term forecasting. The load management techniqueinvolves the simulation, by means of a digital computer, of the behaviourof the power generating system facing different situations of demandand of water inflows, each situation being taken into account along withits probability of taking place. Finally, some considerations are explained,relative to the most important results that are obtained in practiceby the application of the above mentioned method.</TEXT></DOC>